  "text": [
    "My life is vile",
    "I hate it so",
    "I\u2019ll wait awhile",
    "And then I\u2019ll go.",
    "Why wait at all?",
    "Hope springs alive,",
    "Good may befall",
    "I yet may thrive.",
    "It is because I can\u2019t make up my mind",
    "If God is good, impotent or unkind."
  ],
